  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CsvFileDataSource
    An CsvFileDataSource stores facts in the CSV format inside a file of the extension .csv.
    FileDataSource
    A FileDataSource is an abstract implementation of a storage for fact terms in a file of some format.
    QueryResultIterator
    Iterates trough all answers to a query.
    RdfFileDataSource
    An RdfFileDataSource stores facts in the RDF N-Triples format inside a file of the extension .nt.
    SparqlQueryResultDataSource
    A SparqlQueryResultDataSource provide the results of a SPARQL query on a given web endpoint.
